[中文]
简明编译教程：
1. 同步此仓库于并放置于patch_device/hwu9508/目录下；
2. 切换到miui_recovery目录，输入命令：
    . build/envsetup.sh
    make -j4 u9508
3. 将会在out/patch_device/u9508/目录下看见miui recovery
4. 其他，经过修改后的miui recovery源代码见https://github.com/scue/miui_recovery_hwU8950d；
5. 其他，最初的Miui recovery源代码见https://github.com/MiCode/miui_recovery
6. 目前海思平台的荣耀2还不可以直接运行MIUI recovery，海思平台的recovery打包方法有所不同。

[English]
HOW-TO:
1. sync this repository to $MIUI_RECOVERY_TOPDIR/patch_device/hwu9508/;
2. cd $MIUI_RECOVERY_TOPDIR/, type commands as following:
    . build/envsetup.sh
    make -j4 u9508
3. you can get miui recovery in out/patch_device/u9508/
4. otherwise, had modified src: https://github.com/scue/miui_recovery_hwU8950d；
5. otherwise, origin miui recovery src: https://github.com/MiCode/miui_recovery
6. Huawei Honor2(board platform:hisilicon-k3) can't run this compiled MIUI recovery, lack unpack bootimg tool for hisilicon platform.
